SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4157
A bill to amend 1979 PA 94, entitled
"The state school aid act of 1979,"
by amending sections 11, 104, 104b, and 104c (MCL 388.1611,
388.1704, 388.1704b, and 388.1704c), section 11 as amended by 2024
PA 148, section 104 as amended by 2024 PA 120, section 104b as
amended by 2018 PA 265, and section 104c as amended by 2021 PA 48,
and by adding section 104d.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
